{
  "stem": "8962.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I think that was in 1934 or '35 already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "By that time, he decided he had to make a living, and he was very handy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the cars then did not come with ashtrays and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And plastic was then coming on the market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Only it was called Bakelite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he took forms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he built ashtrays that could be hung into the doors and flower vases and this kind of accessories for the car.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he set up a little factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he went out, and he sold them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he had a secretary who was also Gentile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he had to get rid of her because as a Jew he was not allowed to work with a Gentile person.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And by that time already, people around us were being arrested and shipped to Dachau and to other places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we, of course, immediately, we were trying to say, let's go to America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my father said, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We're not going to America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This Hitler is not going to last just like the other chancellors never lasted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He's not going to last.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I'm not leaving this country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I fought here in the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My brother died in the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we've been here for hundreds of years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We're not leaving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "This is our country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But as time went, it became worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So when he had this little factory, one day somebody came in and said, Julius, you better watch out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They're coming.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So he tried to sell the business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And he found somebody in Hamburg who had decided he wanted to buy the businesses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "This was a good business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he sold all the equipment.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
